name: Remember the Past
description:
This is one of the card collection series that I will release in this nft edition.
and this series is specially made for Hicetnunc.

This card collection series tells about daily activity, friendship and social culture.

Series no.9 " Remember the Past "

This card tells the story of a moment where a father takes his family to see a photo book that reminds them of a memory in the past that they had done together.
